vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting an amendment to Planned Development District No. 49 at the northwest corner of East Camp Wisdom Road and University Hills Boulevard
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval, subject to a revised conceptual plan, a street section, and revised conditions
